WEBVTT

00:00.133 --> 00:01.301
<i>Clay, you have what's called
a dissociative fugue disorder.</i>

00:01.302 --> 00:03.387
You temporarily become
someone else.

00:03.388 --> 00:04.763
Why is there a kid here?

00:04.764 --> 00:06.139
He lost his parents.

00:06.140 --> 00:08.221
He stays with us sometimes.
We try to help him.

00:08.222 --> 00:09.356
I'm Clay.

00:09.357 --> 00:10.559
Logan.

00:10.560 --> 00:11.978
I just fell off that stupid bike
you gave me, that's all.

00:11.979 --> 00:13.429
Well, let me see.

00:13.430 --> 00:15.148
Does your mom
know about this?

00:15.149 --> 00:17.859
No. And you can't
tell her, okay?

00:17.860 --> 00:21.238
Okay, it looks like Natan Scott
<i>was</i> on flight 2326 last night.

00:21.239 --> 00:24.324
I just want to go about
my business and live my life.

00:25.408 --> 00:26.647
I'm sorry
for what I done to you.

00:26.648 --> 00:28.495
How's that for a comeback, huh?

00:36.193 --> 00:38.046
Good news.

00:38.047 --> 00:39.881
We've reached
new financial agreement.

00:39.882 --> 00:42.433
So they send
more money...

00:44.804 --> 00:46.221
and then you die.

