02:29.821 --> 02:33.124
♪ now she's walking down the aisle ♪
Can I please have an application?

02:33.125 --> 02:34.996
Sure...

02:36.580 --> 02:38.458
They say I need a job
now I'm on parole.

02:38.459 --> 02:41.701
I guess they didn't find
your little speech

02:41.702 --> 02:43.755
as moving as I did.

02:43.756 --> 02:48.635
So, what do you say?
I'll be the best employee ever.

02:48.636 --> 02:50.720
That position
has been filled.

02:50.721 --> 02:52.639
I just watched you
put up that sign.

02:52.640 --> 02:55.934
Well, now you can watch me
take it down.

02:55.935 --> 02:58.562
Have a nice day.

02:58.563 --> 03:00.454
Have a nice day.

